narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Definitely take it if you love traveling or you like sociology. Take it if you want to improve your writing and speaking, or force yourself to read some interesting articles about city. Take it if you are interested in public management or policies, and want to make cities better places to live.

ENGL 114 03 is great for anyone with a love of urban studies, global studies, or any sort of social studies. You learn so much about writing, and in many cases you have the opportunity to write about what you wish to write about.
